{"tid":1780611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國或如期周日對中國商品加徵關稅","createTime":"2019-12-12T13:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T00:27:28.000Z","uid":165683,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2d74d6f1c17d54c0850bc7dc94be15ebefeb1a","tid":1780611,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"美國對約1600億美元中國貨加徵15%關稅的期限下周日屆滿。路透社報道，總統特朗普星期四與貿易代表萊特希澤、財長努欽等幕僚開會。報道引述消息指，華府可能會如期加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士又指，如果美國加徵新一輪關稅，特朗普在餘下任期內，可能不會再與中國進行貿易談判。<br />\n<br />\n中美雙方目前仍未就首階段貿易協議的關鍵部分達成共識，包括中方承諾購買美國農產品的規模，以及美國何時取消之前對中國商品已加徵的其他關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497378-20191212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497378-20191212.htm&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=bbb59531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497378-20191212.htm&h=44a767c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497378-20191212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c0bbc6db04bef5f987e1a7ab729fa3e3840e244c","tid":1780611,"uid":338743,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"484d1f321464767166de03d701ce931bce0105a1","tid":1780611,"uid":165683,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c0bbc6db04bef5f987e1a7ab729fa3e3840e244c","tid":1780611,"uid":338743,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"青山熱血派注意 ...."},{"pid":"f118f623d34d5d61ebc4e958ade006ee0f98b845","tid":1780611,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ef7e095a13ddba9ed9ea85569a6c26082911a03d","tid":1780611,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"P